    #ReaddyAI #BuildFaster #NoCode 
`,template2:`My mind is blown! 🤯 {raaddyaccount} just auto-generated my {projectname} for me. The future of building is here. 

    See what it made: {projectsharelink} 

    Want to try? {referrallink} 

    #ReaddyAI #AI #Innovation`,template3:`Shipped {projectname} in record time with {raaddyaccount}. Idea to done, just like that.
    Preview: {projectsharelink} 

    Join me and build something: {referrallink} 

    #ReaddyAI #Productivity #Maker`,template4:`Got ideas but no dev team? Same. So I used {raaddyaccount} to bring {projectname} to life myself.
    See how: {projectsharelink} 

    Start building: {referrallink} 

    #ReaddyAI #ProblemSolving #Startups`,template5:`So proud of this! With a little help from {raaddyaccount}, I've just launched {projectname} into the world.
    Explore it: {projectsharelink} 

    Create your own: {referrallink} 

    #ReaddyAI #BuildingInPublic #IndieHacker`,template6:`No heavy lifting required. {raaddyaccount} just built {projectname} for me while I sipped my coffee. ☕️
    Peek at it: {projectsharelink} 

    Build effortlessly: {referrallink} 

