r: #5A30F7;">Readdy Booking</span>',description:"Set up booking calendars, manage availability, and handle appointments in Readdy. Let your visitors book services directly on your website, all in one seamless experience."},"credit-guard":{title:'<span style="color: #5A30F7;">Credit Care</span>',description:"Protect your credits when exploring AI generations. Discard unsatisfactory results, restore previous versions, and get your credits back. Credit Care usage resets monthly."},community:{title:'<span style="color: #5A30F7;">Community</span>',description:'Join the new <span style="font-weight: 700;">Readdy Community</span> to connect with fellow Readdy-ers! Share your work and experiences, ask questions, offer feedback. Be part of the conversation, learn from each other, and grow together — all within the Readdy community.'},"quick-edit":{title:'<span style="color: #5A30F7;">Quick Edit</span>',description:'Update what you see, where you see it. <span style="font-weight: 700;">Quick Edit</span> lets you make inline changes to text, links, and images in Preview. Review and send all changes at once to stay in control.'}},cH={"team-collaboration":{title:'<span style="color: #5A30F7;">Collaboration</span>',description:"Team Collaboration is now available! You can invite members to join your project via email or invitation link. Team members can view and edit within the same project, and project owners can manage editing permissions for each member."},"project-notification-email":{title:'<span style="color: #5A30F7;">Project Email</span>',description:'Configure <span style="font-weight: 700;">notification emails for each project independently</span>. Receive form submissions to different email addresses for different projects, making it easier to manage multiple projects and collaborate with teams.'}},dH={resend:{title:'<span style="color: #5A30F7;">Resend</span>',description:'Send form notification emails from <span style="font-weight: 700;">your own custom domain</span> with Resend integration. Customize sender name, email address, and subject line to match your brand identity and improve email deliverability.'}},uH={"social-media":{title:'<span style="color: #5A30F7;">AI Social Posts</span>',description:'AI taps into the latest trends to craft posts tailored to your website, and publishes to <span style="font-weight: 700;">Facebook, Instagram, X, and LinkedIn</span> in one click. Help more people discover your site.'}},pH={"file-upload-parsing":{title:'<span style="color: #5A30F7;">File Upload & Parsing</span>',description:'Upload PDFs, spreadsheets, text files, and images directly in project creation or chat. AI can read <span style="font-weight: 700;">PDF, CSV, XLSX, and TXT</span> to turn requirements and data into pages, while other files stay available as project assets.'}},fH={"referral-rewards":{title:'<span style="color: #5A30F7;">Referral Rewards</span>',description:'Invite a new friend to Readdy and once they sign up and subscribe, <span style="font-weight: 700;">both of you get 2,500 credits</span>.',action:"Invite now"}},mH={"project-transfer":{title:'<span style="color: #5A30F7;">Project Transfer</span>',description:'Project Transfer lets you move a project from one Readdy account to another. This is useful when you need to <span style="font-weight: 700;">hand a project over to a client</span>, a teammate, or another account you own.'}},hH={shop:{title:'<span style="color: #5A30F7;">Shop</span>',description:'Turn your website into a ready-to-sell online store with <span style="font-weight: 700;">Import Products</span>, <span style="font-weight: 700;">Manage Inventory</span>, and <span style="font-weight: 700;">Receive Orders</span> all in one place.'}},gH={$comment:tH,moreReleaseNotes:nH,buttonGotIt:sH,buttonLearnMore:oH,newFeatures:aH,v1:iH,v3:rH,v4:lH,v5:cH,v6:dH,v7:uH,v9:pH,v10:fH,v11:mH,v12:hH},vH="All keys in this file are prefixed with: dashboard",yH={title:"My Projects",empty:"No projects yet. Create your firs