their plan in the next billing cycle`,siteDiagnosis:"Analyze your website for SEO issues, performance problems, and security vulnerabilities.",readdyAgentVoice:"Website visitors can ask about business info or book appointments by speaking.",readdyAgentChat:"Website visitors can send chat messages to inquire about business details and book or manage appointments.",formSubmissions:"Limits the total number of form submissions you can receive per month across all forms."}},d0e={monthlyCreditsLeft:"Monthly Credits Left",remainingTotalCredits:"Remaining / Total Credits",creditsResetOn:"Credits reset on",creditsLeft:"Credits Left",totalCredits:"Total Credits",resetOn:"Reset on",plan:"Plan",gracePeriodTooltip:"Renew your subscription to restore features related to credit usage. Otherwise, your account will revert to the Free plan.",unlimitedCreditTooltip:"Approximately ${credits} in value has been used up",unlimitedCredits:"Used / Total Credits",monthlyCreditUsage:"Monthly credit usage",yearlyCreditUsage:"Yearly credit usage"},u0e={title:"Frequently Asked Questions",creditsWhat:{question:"What are credits and how do they work?",answer:"Credits are your design currency in Readdy. Each generation or edit costs 25 credits. For a detailed breakdown of how credits are used across different features, please refer to Credit Consumption Rules. <br>Credits refresh automatically every month for all users, whether you're on a monthly or annual plan. The exact refresh date depends on your subscription start date and can be viewed on your Subscription page."},creditsRunOut:{question:"What happens when I run out of credits?",answer:"When you use up all your available credits, you can upgrade to a higher subscription plan to receive more. If you're already on the highest tier, please contact us at hi{'@'}readdy.ai for additional credit options."},websiteAccess:{question:"Can my published website still be accessed if I cancel my subscription?",answer:"No. Once your subscription expires, your published website will no longer be accessible online. However, don't worry — your project will remain safely stored in your account, and you can republish it anytime after renewing your subscription."},planChange:{question:"Can I upgrade or downgrade my plan?",answer:"Yes, you can upgrade or downgrade at any time, subject to the following rules:<ul><li> - <strong>Upgrades take effect immediately.</strong> Your current billing cycle ends and a new one begins. The remaining value of your current plan is applied as a credit toward the new plan — you only pay the difference. Remaining value is calculated based on your unused Token balance, not the time remaining on your plan.</li><li>- <strong>Downgrades take effect at the start of your next billing cycle.</strong> You'll continue to enjoy your current plan benefits until then.</li><li>- <strong>Some changes may not be available.</strong> If you're on a Yearly plan or multi-year plan, you cannot upgrade to a shorter-cycle higher-tier plan until your current Token value is fully consumed. For multi-year plans, downgrades or cycle changes can only be scheduled during the final year of your subscription due to billing constraints — however, if you've consumed all your Token value during a non-final year, you can reset your subscription period to start the next year early.</li></ul>"},invoices:{question:"Do you provide invoices?",answer:"Yes. All invoices can be viewed and downloaded as PDF files from your Subscription page, making it easy to keep track of your billing records."},companyInvoice:{question:"Can I subscribe and get an invoice under my company name?",answer:`Yes. When making a payment, simply check the "I'm purchasing as a business" option and fill in your company details. The invoice will then be issued under your company name automatically.`}},p0e={title:"Want to switch to {plan} plan?",subtitle:"Here is what will change if you switch",switchTo:"Switch to {plan}",switchToPlanPeriod:"Switch to {plan} {period} Plan",stayOnPlan:"Stay on Current Plan",feedback:{title:"Why are you switching plan?",subtitle:"Help us understand how we can do better",selectPrompt:"Please select all that apply:",placeholder:"Please specify",budgetConsiderations:"Budget considerations (too expensive)",notEnoughValue:"Not getting enough value from current plan",notNeedManyCredits:"I don't need that many credits",other:"Other"},warning:{unlimited:"Unlimited",creditsDecrease:"Credit limit will decrease from {currentCredits} to {nextCredits} per month",projectsDecrease:"Project limit will decrease from unlimited to 10",voiceDecrease:"Leads capture via Readdy Voice Agent will decrease from {currentVoiceLimit} to {nextVoiceLimit} minutes per month",chatDecrease:"Leads capture via Readdy Chat Agent will decrease from {currentChatLimit} to {nextChatLimit} per month",formDecrease:"Form submission limit will decrease from {currentFormLimit} to {nextFormLimit} per month",websiteDeploymentDecrease:"Website deployment limit will decrease from {currentCount} to {nextCount}",billingPeriodMonthly:"monthly",billingPeriodYearly:"yearly",billingPeriodNYears:"{n}-year",loseYearlyDiscount:"Lose the 40% off yearly billing discount",loseBillingDiscount:"Lose the {discount}% off {period} billing discount",priceChange:"Monthly subscribe price will change from ${currentPrice} to ${nextPrice}"},successMessage:"You've successfully switched to the {planName} {interval} plan.<br> Your current plan stays active until {expirationDate}"},f0e={manage:{title:"Manage Subscription",description:"You can switch to the Free Plan at any time. Your current plan will be canceled at the end of your billing cycle.",lowerPlanDescription:"You can switch to a lower plan that better suits your needs. The change will take effect after the current billing cycle ends, on {expirationDate}.",switchToPlan:"Switch to {planName} {interval}",highestPlanDescription:"You are on the highest plan tier. Feel free to contact us if you need more credit.",switchToFree:"Switch to Free",scheduledSwitch:"You've scheduled a switch to the {planName} {interval} plan. It will take effect on next billing cycle, starting on {expirationDate}."},tip:{title:"Manage Subscription",description:"You can switch to the plan that best suits your needs. It will take effect after current billing cycle ends, on {expirationDate}.",continueButton:"Continue to Switch Plan",gotItButton:"Got it"},rights:{title:"Are you sure you want to switch to Free?",subtitle:"You're about to lose access to premium features",betterPrice:"You're on a better-value old price",betterPriceDesc:"Once downgraded, it's gone forever",learnMore:"Learn more",websiteOffline:"Your websites will Go Offline",websiteOfflineDesc:"Customers won't be able to find or visit your site",noLeads:"No longer receive information from visitors",noLeadsDesc:"You'll stop receiving new leads or inquiries",noExporting:"Exporting will no longer be available",noExportingDesc:"You won't be able to reuse your content elsewhere"},feedback:{title:"Could you tell us why you're switching to Free?",subtitle:"Help us understand how we can do better",selectPrompt:"Please select all that apply:",placeholder:"Please tell us a bit more",helpText:"Something not working as expected? If you're facing any issues or need help, we're here for you.",letsTalk:"Let's talk first.",missingFeatures:"Missing desired features",budgetConsiderations:"Budget considerations (Too expensive)",unsatisfied:"Unsatisfied with generated results",switchedToAlternative:"Switched to an alternative",technicalIssues:"Technical bugs/usage issues",noNeed:"No immediate need",revisionsDontMeet:"Revisions don't meet expectations",other:"Other (please specify)"},yearly:{title:"Wait! Save up to",discount:"40%",subtitle:"by switching to the yearly plan",switchButton:"Switch to Yearly Plan",noThanks:"No, thanks"},downgrade:{title:"Let's talk before you go",subtitle:"We'd love to understand how we can serve you better",chatTitle:"15 min chat w