h your email setup before website generation is done. Once your prospect websites are ready, Readdy can move straight into campaign launch and email analysis without asking you to configure everything again.",apiKeyLabel:"Instantly API Key",apiKeyPlaceholder:"Paste your Instantly API Key",helperLink:"How to find your Instantly API Key",connectButton:"Connect",connecting:"Connecting...",skipButton:"Skip, generate first",connectedTag:"Connected",connectedDescription:"{count} mailbox(es) are available in your Instantly workspace.",invalidKey:"Please enter a valid Instantly API Key.",confirmTitle:"Generate {count} websites?",confirmConnectDescription:"This will use {cost} Credits. You can keep editing Cold Email after generation starts.",confirmSkipDescription:"This will use {cost} Credits. You can connect Instantly later in Cold Email.",confirmContinue:"Generate",confirmCancel:"Back",interruptTitle:"A generation task is already running",interruptDescription:"Starting a new generation will interrupt the task that is currently running. Do you want to continue?",interruptConfirm:"Continue"},Q0e={completed:"{done} / {total} completed",total:"Total",success:"Success",running:"Running",failed:"Failed",pending:"Pending",cancel:"Cancel",downloadResults:"Download",backToList:"Back to List",filterAll:"All",filterDone:"Success",filterFailed:"Failed",filterPending:"Pending",continueGen:"Continue",browserWarningStrong:"Please do not close the browser",browserWarningRest:"while generation is in progress",previous:"Previous",quotaExhaustedBanner:"This task paused because your current Outreach quota has been fully used. Upgrade or wait for the next billing cycle to continue.",quotaRecoveredBanner:"Your Outreach quota is available again. You can continue this task from the remaining prospects.",planRequiredBanner:"This task paused because Outreach Campaign now requires a paid plan. Upgrade to continue."},U0e={pending:"Pending",creating:"Creating",generating:"Generating",sharing:"Gettin